summoning_condition.en: This card's name becomes "Jest of the Cosmos Princess" while in the hand.

requirement.en: If you have 5 or more Galaxy Type monsters in your Graveyard, place 1 card from your hand on the bottom of the Deck.

effect.en: Fusion Summon a monster Galaxy Type monster with 1900 or 2600 DEF by shuffling up to 3 Galaxy Type monsters from your field and/or Graveyard into the owner's Deck as material.
